com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport

Class ItemChangeInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport.ItemChangeInfo

  • public final class ItemChangeInfo
extends Object
    Contains information about an Item that has been changed by a command. This information includes the up-to-date ItemIdentifierAndVersion, and details of any changed Cards.
    Since:
    1.0
